                <h2>Robotics Program</h2>
                <p>Our Robotics Program is designed for students eager to explore the world of robotics. This hands-on program teaches the basics of robot design, construction, and programming. Students will work with various sensors and motors to build functional robots, learning about mechanical systems, electronics, and coding.</p>
                <h3>What You Will Learn:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Robot design and construction principles</li>
                    <li>How to program robots using languages like Python and C++</li>
                    <li>Working with sensors, actuators, and microcontrollers</li>
                    <li>Understanding the applications of robotics in industries like healthcare and manufacturing</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Program Benefits:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Develop problem-solving and critical thinking skills</li>
                    <li>Enhance teamwork and collaboration</li>
                    <li>Work on real-world robotics projects</li>
                    <li>Prepare for careers in robotics, engineering, and automation</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#robotics" class="program-btn">Learn More About Robotics</a>
            </div>
