                <h2>Artificial Intelligence Program</h2>
                <p>Our Artificial Intelligence (AI) Program introduces students to the core concepts of AI and machine learning. This program covers the fundamentals of AI, from neural networks and deep learning to real-world applications such as natural language processing, image recognition, and autonomous systems.</p>
                <h3>What You Will Learn:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>The basics of AI, machine learning, and data science</li>
                    <li>How to build and train neural networks</li>
                    <li>Applying AI to solve complex problems in various industries</li>
                    <li>Explore ethical considerations in AI development</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Program Benefits:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Get hands-on experience with AI tools and platforms like TensorFlow</li>
                    <li>Build AI models and apply them to real-world scenarios</li>
                    <li>Learn the impact of AI on industries such as healthcare, finance, and transportation</li>
                    <li>Prepare for careers in AI development, data science, and machine learning engineering</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#ai" class="program-btn">Learn More About AI</a>
            </div>
            <div class="program-image">
                <img src="../image/AI.jpg" alt="AI Program">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Program 3: Coding -->
        <div class="program">
            <div class="program-text">
                <h2>Coding Program</h2>
                <p>Our Coding Program equips students with the essential programming skills needed for today's tech-driven world. From web development and app creation to advanced algorithms, students will learn to code in popular languages like Python, JavaScript, and HTML/CSS. This program is ideal for beginners and advanced learners looking to deepen their coding skills.</p>
                <h3>What You Will Learn:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Programming fundamentals using Python, JavaScript, and C++</li>
                    <li>Web development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript) and mobile app development</li>
                    <li>How to build games, apps, and dynamic websites</li>
                    <li>Debugging, testing, and optimizing code for performance</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>Program Benefits:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Hands-on coding experience with real-world projects</li>
                    <li>Develop problem-solving and computational thinking skills</li>
                    <li>Build a strong portfolio to showcase to future employers</li>
                    <li>Prepare for careers in software development, web development, and IT</li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#coding" class="program-btn">Learn More About Coding</a>
